OL,3,C4-year-old's death by antique cast
OL,4,Croller was an accident, inquest rules
OL,6,FAn inquest has ruled the death of a
OL,7,Ffour-year-old boy while playing with
OL,8,Fan antique cast iron roller in the
OL,9,Fgarden was an accident.
OL,11,FThe Welsh Air Ambulance attended and
OL,12,Fattempted to resuscitate Maldwyn
OL,13,F"Gwern" Evans, but he died at his home
OL,14,Fin Tynreithyn, near Tregaron, in June.
OL,16,FGwern was taken to Glangwili General
OL,17,FHospital in Carmarthen where a post-
OL,18,Fmortem examination was carried out
OL,19,Fwhich confirmed the young boy had a
OL,20,Fsignificant head injury and fractures
OL,21,Fto the skull.
