OL,3,C4-year-old's death by antique cast
OL,4,Croller was an accident, inquest rules
OL,6,FFrom the working diagnosis of the
OL,7,FWelsh Air Ambulance team, the inquest
OL,8,Fheard Gwern had "suffered traumatic
OL,9,Fcardiac arrest secondary to a
OL,10,Fcatastrophic, traumatic brain injury."
OL,12,FThe roller, which is thought to have
OL,13,Fweighed between 50kg and 60kg, had
OL,14,Fbeen kept in the family garden for
OL,15,Faround two years but was moved to
OL,16,Fanother position a fortnight before
OL,17,Fthe accident.
