OL,3,C4-year-old's death by antique cast
OL,4,Croller was an accident, inquest rules
OL,6,FAs there were no witnesses, Senior
OL,7,FCoroner Peter Brunton concluded it was
OL,8,Flikely "Gwern had been able to push
OL,9,Fthe roller from behind and was then
OL,10,Fcarried forward.
OL,12,F"He likely held on to the roller to
OL,13,Ftry and stop it but lost control.
OL,15,F"As it rolled down a slope and hit the
OL,16,Fpatio, the handle likely threw Gwern
OL,17,Fover and he hit the concrete surface."
