OL,3,C4-year-old's death by antique cast
OL,4,Croller was an accident, inquest rules
OL,6,FGwern's mother Sian Eleri Evans
OL,7,Frecounted in a statement how her son
OL,8,Fand daughter had been eating an ice
OL,9,Fcream before Gwern was playing out in
OL,10,Fthe garden. Mrs Evans said she was in
OL,11,Fthe kitchen at the time when she heard
OL,12,Fa thud and rushed out to the garden.
OL,14,FShe later said: "Loss has been
OL,15,Funimaginable, to myself, his father
OL,16,Fand sister, but to the wider family
OL,17,Fand friends."
